{"tid":1888334,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"容海恩指毛孟靜出言侮辱她「低智商」 計劃提出譴責議案","createTime":"2020-02-20T06:40:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-20T14:12:02.000Z","uid":212626,"like":56,"dislike":144,"uniUserReply":136,"replies":[{"pid":"38a208b8c68794e2c1d5b2d511c61c1187b9f941","tid":1888334,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T06:40:42.000Z","msg":"議會陣線立法會議員毛孟靜去年12月於保安事務委員會會議上選舉正副主席時，指新民黨容海恩快將分娩，應撤回其參選副主席的提名。容海恩計劃對議會陣線毛孟靜提出譴責議案。<br />\n<br />\n容海恩表示，毛孟靜辯稱希望她分娩後有足夠時間休息，進一步出言侮辱她低智商，構成性別歧視、孕婦歧視和家庭崗位歧視，屬行為不檢及立下極壞榜樣，完全不符市民期望。<br />\n<br />\n她又強調，毛孟靜如果不是受特權法保障，或會被控告。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2382204/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2382204%2F&d=vOjfDEnLED7uJ%2BqF6s3OfTMRYSN2ZvgGkER1Jhb0l7M%3D&h=bc1e5fad\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2382204/</a>"},{"pid":"5c334d55019455f3b54e46a1fba209f081ec21d3","tid":1888334,"uid":194326,"like":223,"dislike":3,"score":220,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T06:41:17.000Z","msg":"話你戇鳩驚你嬲"},{"pid":"6c674069e0a72f75d2b374d75a64a70acdd521e2","tid":1888334,"uid":2772,"like":122,"dislike":3,"score":119,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T06:41:43.000Z","msg":"形容你都叫侮辱"},{"pid":"3f8f9a3ec8e4e7f0c5cbfdd39c7c7045094dc87a","tid":1888334,"uid":212626,"like":72,"dislike":4,"score":68,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T06:42:07.000Z","msg":"事實都唔講得<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2228a1ffed658346d8ce58d781e62a4f66b3806","tid":1888334,"uid":37869,"like":83,"dislike":4,"score":79,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T06:42:28.000Z","msg":"「完全不符市民期望」<br />\n少數派已完真係啦知個醜字點寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"222cea43446d838903ca72827a2bf9e1aa4b14d6","tid":1888334,"uid":140793,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T06:42:51.000Z","msg":"客觀事實喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/p